Kup: Well if the computer sayd he is clear, then you can let him out. Now tell me what these symptoms are exactly... 
 Rudra656@... wrote: ::Aerotaur:: 
      He nods at Kup.  "Sir, there is something you need to know about the disease the girl escaped from.  It is known only as The Plague.  It's effects are both swift and deadly.  Fortunately it's deadliness eventually killed it off enough for those of my time to develop a vaccine.  Unfortunately she is from a few decades before my time.  She doesn't appear to be infected however."  He pauses for a moment.  "There were rumored accounts, nothing was ever confirmed mind you, but I have heard stories of carriers.  Some have been infected but survive without symptoms for some unknown reason.  There is a way to test."  He thinks to himself for a moment.  "First, if Windlord hasn't been bitten, get him out of there.  There's something in the bite that transmits the disease.  Then I need to borrow an expendable maintenance drone."
